const String kCureFitText =
    'cure.fit is a mobile app that takes a holistic approach towards health and fitness by bringing together all aspects of a healthy lifestyle on a single platform.\n\ncure.fit offers both online and offline experiences across fitness, nutrition and mental wellbeing through its 4 products, i.e, cult.fit, eat.fit, mind.fit & care.fit.\n\nWith the aim to make fitness fun and easy, cult.fit gives workouts a whole new meaning with a range of trainer-led, group workout classes. eat.fit makes healthy eating, easy & affordable. Every eat.fit meal is cooked fresh with the best ingredients and is calorie counted and delivered to your doorstep. Addressing the core aspect of mental wellbeing, mind.fit aims to bring about a lifestyle change and focuses on relieving day to day stress and improving overall mental wellbeing through yoga, guided meditation & 1:1 Therapy. care.fit is a state-of-the-art medical and diagnostic centre that offers doctor consultations and clinical expertise to help in providing care for common illnesses and complex issues. Live your life to the fullest and #BeBetterEveryday';

const String kAirbnbText =
    'Airbnb, Inc. (pronounced /ˈɛərbiːɛnbiː/ AIR-bee-ehn-bee and stylized as airbnb) is an American vacation rental online marketplace company based in San Francisco, California, United States. Airbnb offers arrangement for lodging, primarily homestays, or tourism experiences. The company does not own any of the real estate listings, nor does it host events; it acts as a broker, receiving commissions from each booking.The company was conceived after its founders rented out an air mattress in their living room, effectively turning their apartment into a bed and breakfast, to offset the high cost of rent in San Francisco. Airbnb is a shortened version of its original name, AirBedandBreakfast.com';

